'''Charon''' language was a communication system used by the [[Charon/Legends|Charon]] species. Being [[arachnoid]] creatures, Charon "spoke" by rubbing their mandibles with one another, causing clicks, squeals and scratches. Scientists who analyzed it concluded that the language could only be reproduced by other insectoid species, or by specially programmed [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droids]]. The Charon language had a [[Written Charon language|written form]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

